                     <interp inst="t18200412-81-person738" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             re-examined. The prisoner is no relation of mine at all. His father's name is 
               <persName id="t18200412-81-person739">
                  John 
                  Roberts
               <interp inst="t18200412-81-person739" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-81-person739" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-81-person739" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , and so is mine, but he was not related to me. We have no servants in the house.</p>
